I have removed the assertion that his proof is correct. This is as it was before, with a ref to the USC statement and an update of the Arxiv ref.

What needs to happen is that this should be edited back so that the reference is only to the claim. I am reverting because it is not acceptable to remove entirely all reference to Fokas's claim.
